In the years 1976–1980 he studied at the 2nd degree music school in Pristina ( double bass and music theory class ), and then he studied at the Academy of Music in Pristina (Faculty of Music Theory), graduating in 1987.
In 1988-1990 he continued his music studies in Maribor , but he had to interrupt them and in 1991 he came to Poland.

He completed post-graduate studies in 1996–1999 under the supervision of Krzysztof Penderecki.
